{"tid":1488813,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彭斯警告中國 若想達貿易協議須尊重港法律","createTime":"2019-08-19T16:56:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T02:45:43.000Z","uid":68738,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"665993bacb49b656dad8ee5a247ee0a4eefee34b","tid":1488813,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:56:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190820/large/1566231667_140d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190820%2Flarge%2F1566231667_140d.jpg&h=e1f05daf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n繼美國總統特朗普周日明確將中美貿易談判與香港問題掛鈎後，美國副總統彭斯周一重申一次特朗普的警告。<br />\n<br />\n彭斯表示，北京必須恪守各項承諾，包括《中英聯合聲明》，尊重香港法律的完整性，美國方可與中國達成協議。他說，特朗普政府會繼續敦促北京與香港示威者和平化解分歧。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普周日評論香港局勢時警告中國，一旦香港出現1989年「天安門式」鎮壓，將損害貿易談判，表明「如果他們行使暴力，我的意思是另一次天安門事件，我認為很難跟他們談判貿易協議」。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普政府對香港局勢的關注與日俱增，中國官媒《環球時報》英文版的社論，指華府不能左右中國在香港問題上的決策。社論指，「美國的政治與輿論精英縱能唆使香港激進示威者，但他們絕對不能影響北京對香港情勢的決策」。<br />\n<br />\n路透社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190820/59950886\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190820%2F59950886&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAEPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=26337c9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190820%2F59950886&h=5f32ed0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190820/59950886</a>"},{"pid":"7f19ec6ef94f4d536c8909e5039f907c9c9742ed","tid":1488813,"uid":183758,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:58:39.000Z","msg":"環球時報 = on9"},{"pid":"11fd761aa6d44b682ba72a4f4a59f02250e9f8d5","tid":1488813,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f19ec6ef94f4d536c8909e5039f907c9c9742ed","tid":1488813,"uid":183758,"like":5,"dislike":0,"sc